Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========================================Main Text Strat==========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟被称为“悼词的咏手” 的“Flamehaze”的激烈战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜她…得到了新的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及分别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那时的我却没有意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夏娜新的战斗即将逼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去追“银”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是追是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总该有个适度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你自己提出的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是偶然啦 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不是那样的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========================================Title Start==========================================
