Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\an5\pos(416,341)\fs26\i1\bord2\1c&H1512cc\3c&Hcccef2}恋爱与欲望之游泳池畔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========================================Title End  ==========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一大早就这么热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天当然热啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这么提不起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上的训练也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都坚持了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却一点进步都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人与生俱来的天分不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 已经找好了逃跑的借口了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了 到了这个阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要以那种借口退出了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是天分的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你更加努力变得灵活了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等我啊 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank You 池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 池同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为父亲工作的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿到了很多御崎水上乐园的票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正发给班上的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御崎水上乐园就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近才开业的那个“啊~哈”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的泳装 御崎水上乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“啊~哈”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家都会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会很兴奋的 不愧是池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 平井同学你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 泳装怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一起去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做出这种松弛的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得收到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天或者后天一起……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对老师有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领带歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是正的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛会对着这样一张纸傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全懈怠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是游乐园的入场券吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类就是喜欢戏水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以算是理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身心都松懈得不成样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样才一点进步也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水上乐园会像浴室那么舒适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来屋顶一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜整个上午都没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里了 平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻镇的面包店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么又…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口感不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜瓜面包最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是酥脆松软的口感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃便当好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔这样也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起独自一个人吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起边聊边吃感觉吃得更香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的午餐 一直都是便利店买的饭团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 母亲说 男孩子只吃妈妈亲手做的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会有出息的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扯远了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要约坂井去水上乐园的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得池的好意相邀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天 大家一起去水上乐园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方小姐 你说大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说大家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全班同学的话人数太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的各位 以及
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 还有那两位 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井小姐也没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班里的女英雄不去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没法开场了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好吗 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 决定喽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天早上10点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在池家里集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 别迟到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个从以前就老是迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自作主张地决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多事要处理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点对不起绪方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周末不论用什么方法都要把马乔莉姐拖出屋子的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头每天都闷在家里喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把她带去哪里散散心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子 醉得不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:10:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我烂醉如泥的睡美人马乔莉-冬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉如何 这件泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是太惹眼 这种样式的也许比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男生一起去游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能穿那么老土的泳装呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不试穿那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不还衣服给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱情 爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方小姐 饶了我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是这款
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要这件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的连衣裤泳装就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 小夏娜 买到你的泳装了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿学校的泳衣太过于普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过于？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说这是个穿平时在学校不能穿的可爱泳装的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快穿穿看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边等着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙真是记吃不记打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是误会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近有这样的地方 夏天就不愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中和佐藤看来是不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不回电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也不用管他们的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们5人玩开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中双人骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女组合进行水中骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优胜组的奖品是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可观赏夜景的餐厅的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪华大餐免费招待券 以及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手制面包随便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手制面包随便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一起观赏夜景的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你清澈的双眸干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满有意思的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正下午才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然男生还差一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题待会再考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急 别急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让各位期待已久的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香里 and 一美的泳装秀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是由香里小姐 请出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是吉田小姐 请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪…绪方小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头 不要这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不时常出来走动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体会垮掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样出来才是对身体有害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣太 那边是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马乔莉姐 现在真的要进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁愿意忍受这种酷热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以改到明天来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的话有点不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“悼词的咏手”来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悼词的…那个人要来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然刚才没有觉察到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个“Flamehaze”都悠闲地来游泳池玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有些怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下小卖店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头那样说了 不能不听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真衰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是碰上了绪方他们 该怎么解释
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 人这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能随随便便就碰上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是让他们去买瓶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启作和荣太死哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人说去买喝的 不都是骗人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎么回事 拒绝了我的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又会来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你们两人来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我说清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道 我也不大清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来个中原由还满复杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 你只是单纯地来玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没兴趣和你打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想打的话另外找人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吃有喝能美美睡上一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“悼词的咏手”就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悼词的咏手也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了自己作为“Flamehaze”的身份了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对我们来说 是怎么都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 昨天你们说不来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了给大家个惊喜是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 简简单单地就答应的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没那么受注目了 对吧 佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 突然出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想活跃一下气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 田中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然连我也瞒着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们会参加骑马战的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑马战？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 抓到同一根绳子两头的人一组
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的人就做拉拉队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 大姐头还等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办还不都得这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比暴露马乔莉姐的身份要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御崎水上乐园的著名活动项目\N水中双人骑马战 马上开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢到最多头带的一组为优胜组
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不可以落马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池那家伙跑到哪里上厕所去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说了努力为我们加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限定时间内抢到最多头带的那组
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将得到可观赏夜景的饭店的双人餐券
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与坂井同学一起去可观赏夜景的饭店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与坂井同学一起去可观赏夜景的饭店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢的话 甜瓜面包随便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢的话 甜瓜面包随便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗 田中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看你的行动力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必那么紧张 放松些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 火热激烈的水中骑马战即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限定时间为3分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友间相互拼抢也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找别的组抢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一美还真行啊 不过呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑马战毕竟还是要靠脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样有厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 还想来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是佐藤很强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必勉强和他们对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然生存的组也越来越少了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 难得还没出局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在结束之前努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然优胜是没希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一定可以拿到什么奖的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和坂井这么近距离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 平井队行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了 快逃 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在搞什么飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还问你为什么要追过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是赢了我们也没意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是一种锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像他们那样真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 头再低一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我再快一些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香里 该不会是因为我和悠二粘在一起才生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是怎么会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣太 给我加速
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学 他们来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优胜者是拿到5条头带的冈田队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈田老师怎么也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且像那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是他太太吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要追来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:21:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我原因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜每次总这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子 你也喝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头 十分十分的抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.60,0:22:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你一个人扔在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没怪你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了奇怪的东西当枕头 脖子痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今天就在此解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期一又要到学校去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你为什么要追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========================================Next EP Start==========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.00,0:24:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用语言无法传达的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜只身仗剑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.20,0:24:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴着“磷子”的绝叫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.80,0:24:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 城市里新的“徒”们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.10,0:24:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纠缠的思绪
